# Clinic Booking System Database

## 📋 Description

This is a MySQL-based relational database for managing clinic appointments, doctors, patients, services, and payments.

## 🚀 How to Run

1. Install MySQL.
2. Open your SQL client.
3. Run the script in `clinic_booking.sql` to create all tables.

## 🧠 ERD

![ERD Screenshot](./images\erd.png)  
Or view the [ERD here](https://dbdiagram.io/d/clinic-booking-system-ERD-681cddc35b2fc4582fcc01cc)

## 📁 Project Structure

- `clinic_booking.sql`: SQL file with all CREATE TABLE statements.
- `README.md`: This file.
- `erd.png`: ERD image showing relationships.
